{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Grease a square baking tin (20 cm).","Place peanuts in mixing bowl and roughly chop <nobr>1 sec\/speed 7<\/nobr>. Transfer to a bowl and set aside.","Place linseeds in mixing bowl and grind <nobr>1 min\/speed 9<\/nobr>. Transfer to bowl with peanuts and set aside.","Place dates in mixing bowl and finely chop <nobr>6 sec\/speed 7<\/nobr>.","Add puffed rice, oats, cinnamon, salt and reserved chopped peanuts and ground linseeds then mix <nobr>15 sec\/\/speed 4<\/nobr>. Transfer to a large bowl and set aside.","Place peanut butter, agave syrup and butter in mixing bowl then heat <nobr>5 min\/90°C\/speed 1<\/nobr>.","Add vanilla extract and stir <nobr>10 sec\/speed 3<\/nobr>.","Add reserved dry ingredients and mix <nobr>10 sec\/\/speed 4<\/nobr>. Finish mixing by hand with spatula if necessary then transfer to prepared tin. Press down firmly with the back of a spoon then place in fridge to firm up for 1 hour.","Slice into 12 equal-sized bars, wrap in cling film or greaseproof paper and serve or store in fridge for up to 5 days."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["30 g butter, diced, plus extra for greasing","35 g peanuts, roasted, unsalted","30 g linseeds","170 g dates, pitted, halved","30 g puffed rice","90 g rolled oats, quick cook","½ tsp ground cinnamon","1 pinch fine sea salt","130 g smooth peanut butter (unsweetened)","100 g agave syrup","1 tsp vanilla extract"]}],"id":"r143896","imageLink":"https:\/\/1.bp.blogspot.com\/-ISBIMsxzLmQ\/XZap_-PI7gI\/AAAAAAAAhXs\/PW5hnejzY4s0IZ16EssSI8__bTAsqV67wCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_IwjVzxcEW0HIbDr8.png","title":"Peanut Snack Bars","publishedAt":"2017-04-17T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"5 g","fat":"11.1 g","uom":"per 1 piece","carbohydrates":"24.7 g","calories":"916 kJ \/ 219 kcal"},"usefulItems":"square baking tin (20 cm), long sharp knife, cling film, greaseproof paper, refrigerator","hintsAndTricks":["Swap the agave syrup for the same quantity of syrup of your choice, or even runny honey - the recipe will still work."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","1h 30m","12 pieces"]}